title: Fitness Personality Katie Austin
description:
What a weekend! First, there was the innocent family trip to get a pizza that went horribly awry and ended in doggie diarrhea and human vomit. And then there was the recalibrating of Lala’s explorer page, and finally, a lovely re-centering hike with the gusbands! And just comment “Amen!” if you’re ready for Fitness Personality Katie Austin, the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit edition Rookie of 2022! Her feature in the mag drops next month! Katie built her own fitness app, and hosts two shows, her snapchat cooking show, and her podcast, “Austin AF.” She has plenty to say about balance, not being a slave to exercise, healthy habits, and sorta following in the famous footsteps of her mom, fitness queen Denise Austin.
